tog-previewontop: Woneska chiyezgelelo pambele bokosi lakulembamo lindaoneke

tog-fancysig: Tola siginecha ngati ni malemba gha wiki (kwambula kulumikiza ku jani linu)
tog-uselivepreview: Woneska chiyezgelelo kwambula jani kuwa liphya
tog-forceeditsummary: Nichichizgani pala nkhujala kulemba kwambula kulongosola ivyo nasitha (panji kuwezgeleska majalilo gha nyengo zose)

tog-watchlisthideliu: Bisa vyakulemba vya awo ŵana ma akaunti pakuonelela kwane
tog-watchlistreloadautomatically: Welezgaso kuoneska majani gha kuonelela pala kusintha kunyake kwazomelezgeka(pakukhumbika JavaScript)
tog-watchlistunwatchlinks: Sazgapo malemba gha kuonelela/kwambula kuonelela ({{int:Watchlist-unwatch}}/{{int:Watchlist-unwatch-undo}}) ku majani gha kuonelela agho ghasinthika (pakukhumbika JavaScript kuti vyakusintha vyasono vioneke)

tog-watchlisthidepatrolled: Bisa vyakulemba vya majani ghakuzomelezgeka na ŵalongozgi ku majani ghakuonelela
tog-ccmeonemails: Nane niŵeso na makalata gha pa intaneti agho nkhutuma ku ŵanyane
tog-diffonly: Kuoneska yayi ivyo vili pa jani pasi pa vyakupambana viŵili
tog-norollbackdiff: Kuoneska kupambana yayi pala nkhuwezgeleska kumanyuma vyakulemba
tog-useeditwarning: Nichenjezgani pala nkhuleka jani kwambula kusunga ivo nalembanga
tog-prefershttps: Nyengo zose nigwiliske ntchito kulumikiza kwa intaneti kwa chitetezo chikulu pala nili mkati mwa akaunti yane
tog-showrollbackconfirmation: Woneska batani la kusimikizga pala nadofya pakuwezgeleska kumanyazuma kwa uyo wakamalila kulemba
tog-requireemail: Nitumilani kalata yakufwatula pasiwedi pekha pala naika kalata na zina ilo nkhugwiliska ntchito vyapelekeka.

badaccess-groups: Ivo mwate muchite vyakuzomelezgeka ku ŵagwiliski aŵo ŵali mu  {{PLURAL:$2|gulu la|limoza mwa magulu ngati ni}}: $1.
versionrequiredtext:
Mtundu $1 wa MediaWiki ukukhumbika kuti mugwiliske ntchito jani ili.
Wonani [[Special:Version|mtundu wa jani]].
feed-invalid: Ivo mwalondezga kuti muonenge vikumanyikwa yayi.
sort-rowspan-error: Jani lino lina thebulu ilo lina mizele inandi kujumpha unandi wa mizele ya thebulu. Munganozga ivi kwizila mwakusintha jani lino.
nosuchactiontext:
Icho mwate mupange kwizila pa adilesi ya intaneti kulije.
Mukwenela kuti mwangulemba uheni adilesi ya intaneti, panji mwangulondezga linki yambula kwenelela.
Nyengo zinyake ichi chingang'anamulaso kuti sofutiweya iyo {{SITENAME}} ikugwiliska ntchito ina suzgo.
databaseerror-text:
Suzgo lasangika mu databezi.
Ichi chingang'anamula kuti sofutiweya ina suzgo.
enterlockreason: Ikani chifukwa cha kukiyila, kusazgapo na utali wa nyengo apo loko uzamufumilapo
delete-scheduled:
Jani la "$1" lasankhika kuti lifufutikenge mwakuyana na nyengo iyo yathyeka.
Chonde fwasani.
delete-hook-aborted:
Kufufuta kwadumulika na sofutiweya.
Palije kulongosola uko kwapasika.
badtitletext:
Zina la ichi mwapempha palije,panji ntchakusokonekela na viyowoyelo vinyake.
Panji china malemba ghambula kuzomelezgeka mu mitu.

mypreferencesprotected: Mulije chilolezo chakusintha vyakunozgela akaunti yinu.
titleprotected: Mutu uwu ulikukanizgika kulembeka na [[User:$1|$1]]. Chifukwa chakupelekeka ntchakuti $2.
exception-nologin-text: Chonde njilani mu akaunti kuti musinthe panji kuchita icho mwate muchite.
cannotlogoutnow-text: Kufuma mu akaunti nkhwamachitiko yayi pala mukugwiliska ntchito $1.
welcomecreation-msg:
Akaunti yinu yapangika.
Mungasintha vyakukhwaskana akaunti yinu pa{{SITENAME}} [[Special:Preferences|vyakunozga]] pala mwakhumba.
prefs-help-yourpassword: Akaunti yinu pala yasokonezeka ingapulumusika. Wonani $1 pala mukukhumba vyakusintha vinyake.
anoneditwarning: Chenjezgo: Mundanjile mu akaunti yinu. Pala mulembenge chilichose IP adilesi yinu waliyose waionenge. Pala [$1 mwanjila] mu akaunti yinu panji [$2 mwapanga akaunti], vyakulemba vinu vyose viŵenge mu zina linu, na uwemi unyake.
blockedtext: Zina linu panji IP address yakanizgika. Walikukanizga ni $1. Chifukwa ntchakuti $2. * kwamba kwakukanizga: $8 *kumala kwa kukanizga: $6 * Intended blockee: $7 Mungafumba $1 panji [[{{MediaWiki:Grouppage-sysop}}|administrator]] zakuti mulongosolelane. Mungagwiliska "{{int:emailuser}}" pala muna email address yinu yojuliskila [[Special:Preferences|preferences]] ndipo njakuti mungaseŵezeska. IP address yinu ni $3, ndipo block ID ni #$5. Chonde sazgani vose ivo vili pachanya pakufumba ovwili.
newarticletext: Mwalondezga link iyo peji lake palije dankha. Kuti mulilembe, yambani kulemba mu box pasi apa (onani [$1 peji laovwili] mwa vinandi). Pala mwizapo mwangozi, dofyani batani la browser winu back.
noarticletext: Palije dankha mazgo pa jani lino. Munga [[Special:Search/{{PAGENAME}}|penja jani lino]] mu viyowoyelo vinyake, [{{fullurl:{{#Special:Log}}|page={{FULLPAGENAMEE}}}} penja mu ma log nghakupokelelapo], panji[{{fullurl:{{FULLPAGENAME}}|action=edit}} yatani jani lino].
noarticletext-nopermission: Pasono palije dankha mazgo ghalighose pa jani lino. Munga [[Special:Search/{{PAGENAME}}|penja mutu uwo]] mu majani ghanyake, panji [{{fullurl:{{#Special:Log}}|page={{FULLPAGENAMEE}}}} mungapenja mu mathala ghanyake], kwene mulije chilolezo chakuyata jani lino.
previewnote: Kumbukilani kuti ichi ntchiyelezgelo waka. Mundazomelezge dankha kusintha!

Kufufutika, kutchinjilizika, na kuthyeka kwa jani ili kuli pasi apa.

nolinkstoimage: Palije majani agho ghogwiliska chinthu ichi.
sharedupload-desc-here:
Chinthu ichi ntchaku $1 ndipo chingagwiliskikaso kunyake.
Vakulongosola vake [$2 file description page] vili pasi apa.
sp-contributions-toponly: woneska vyakulemba ivyo ni mbili iphya
metadata-help:
Chinthu ichi china vyakulemba vinyake ivo panji vikasazgika pa siku ilo kamela ikajambulilanga, panji apo makina gha ghakulemba ghakajambulila.
Pala chinthu chakwamba chasinthika, vyakulemba vinandi vikuukako.
